OL,3,CMan rebailed after death of ice hockey
OL,4,Cstar Adam Johnson
OL,6,FPolice have rebailed a man who was
OL,7,Farrested on suspicion of manslaughter
OL,8,Ffollowing the death of ice hockey
OL,9,Fplayer Adam Johnson.
OL,11,FJohnson was fatally injured when he
OL,12,Fwas hit in the neck by an opposition
OL,13,Fplayer's skate during a match at
OL,14,FSheffield's Utilita Arena on 28
OL,15,FOctober last year.
OL,17,FThe 29-year-old American, who was
OL,18,Fplaying for Nottingham Panthers
OL,19,Fagainst , died in hospital.
