OL,6,FThe incident, which was witnessed by
OL,7,Fthousands of fans inside the stadium,
OL,8,Fshocked the ice hockey world.
OL,10,FA man was arrested on suspicion of
OL,11,Fmanslaughter in November and was
OL,12,Fbailed by South Yorkshire Police.
OL,14,FOn Friday, the force said: "A man who
OL,15,Fwas arrested on suspicion of
OL,16,Fmanslaughter following the death of
OL,17,Fice hockey player Adam Johnson in
OL,18,FSheffield has been rebailed."
