OL,6,FThe statement added: "Adam, aged 29,
OL,7,Fwas seriously injured during a game
OL,8,Fbetween the Sheffield Steelers and
OL,9,FNottingham Panthers on October 28 last
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,F"He was sadly later pronounced
OL,13,Fdeceased in hospital. A post-mortem
OL,14,Fexamination confirmed he died as a
OL,15,Fresult of a neck injury.
OL,17,F"On November 14, a man was arrested on
OL,18,Fsuspicion of manslaughter and later
OL,19,Fbailed. Today, he has been rebailed
OL,20,Funtil April 25 2024.
