OL,6,F"Our investigation is ongoing and our
OL,7,Fthoughts remain with Adam's family at
OL,8,Fthis time."
OL,10,FLast month, Sheffield's senior coroner
OL,11,Fopened an inquest into Johnson's death
OL,12,Fbut suspended her investigation as
OL,13,Fpolice inquiries continue.
OL,15,FIt emerged later that Tanyka Rawden
OL,16,Fhad issued a Prevention of Future
OL,17,FDeaths Report to Ice Hockey UK and the
OL,18,FEnglish Ice Hockey Association (EIHA)
OL,19,Fabout the use of neck guards in the
OL,20,Fsport.
