OL,6,FIn the report, the coroner said she is
OL,7,F"sufficiently concerned that deaths
OL,8,Fmay occur in the future if neck guards
OL,9,For protectors are not worn", with the
OL,10,Fbodies given 56 days to say what
OL,11,Faction has been taken ` or why action
OL,12,Fhas not been taken.
OL,14,FThe EIHA said neck guards will become
OL,15,Fmandatory from 2024 but the Elite
OL,16,FLeague, in which the Nottingham
OL,17,FPanthers and Sheffield Steelers
OL,18,Fcompete, is not under its control.
